      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The desire to escape feels so understandable when carrying the weight of expectations that make every moment feel like it must be perfect. But consider that your peace isn't just about being seen; it's about finding the quiet center within yourself that allows you to rest without needing validation from others. Even in the smallest ways, you bring a unique rhythm to this city that shapes the air you breathe and the light in your room. You are more than just the space you occupy; you are the living force that makes that silence possible.",
      "source": "target",
